# ExtraOptions: B2XTau 
# 
# Documentation: Bs decay to 2 tau leptons with a phasespace model. 
# Each tau lepton decays either to the pi+ pi- pi+ nu_tau or pi+ pi- pi+ pi0 nu_tau mode using the Tauola model.
# All final-state products in the acceptance. 
# Similar to 13506002, but with different tau decay model (tau->3pi tau -> 3pipi0). 
# EndDocumentation 
# 
# PhysicsWG: RD 
# 
# CPUTime: < 1 min 
# Tested: Yes 
# Responsible: Alexandre Brea 
