# Tauola steering options
Define TauolaCurrentOption 1
Define TauolaBR1 1.0
#
Alias Mytau+ tau+ 
Alias Mytau- tau- 
ChargeConj Mytau+ Mytau- 
#
Decay B_s0sig
 1.000 Mytau+ Mytau- PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay anti-B_s0sig 
#
Decay Mytau-
  9.31        TAUOLA 5;
  4.62        TAUOLA 8;
Enddecay
CDecay Mytau+ 
# 
#
End
